            "title": "滬指開市跌不足1點 深成指升36點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段變動不大，上證綜指以4107點開市，跌不足1點或0.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報15157點，則升36點或0.24%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升10點或0.22%，開報4820點；創業板指數開市報3704點，升16點或0.46%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15942033-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e8%b7%8c%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b31%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8736%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-30 09:30:10",
